1
00:00:27,400 --> 00:00:30,040
=Soft-Hearted God=

2
00:00:30,160 --> 00:00:31,759
=Episode 8=
(I know he's a stubborn)

3
00:00:31,760 --> 00:00:33,395
(yet soft-hearted ally.)

4
00:00:44,980 --> 00:00:46,140
General Pei.

5
00:00:49,220 --> 00:00:50,259
Your Highness.

6
00:00:50,260 --> 00:00:52,579
(Qingxin Pavilion)
Aren't you supposed to be on patrol?

7
00:00:52,580 --> 00:00:54,859
What are you doing here
in this shabby mountain shrine?

8
00:00:54,860 --> 00:00:56,459
I heard you were in danger,

9
00:00:56,460 --> 00:00:57,459
so I came.

10
00:00:57,460 --> 00:00:59,500
Did Chu Shan send you?

11
00:01:02,060 --> 00:01:03,500
Yes or no?

12
00:01:03,700 --> 00:01:04,420
Yes.

13
00:01:05,420 --> 00:01:07,100
So he knows I'm alive

14
00:01:07,420 --> 00:01:09,020
and sent you to kill me?

15
00:01:09,340 --> 00:01:10,660
You're courting death.

16
00:01:10,780 --> 00:01:11,980
(Qingxin Pavilion)
Be careful!

17
00:01:13,340 --> 00:01:14,880
Where did this wandering sorcerer
come from?

18
00:01:14,880 --> 00:01:15,820
Protect Her Highness!

19
00:01:33,260 --> 00:01:34,180
Insolence!

20
00:01:36,540 --> 00:01:37,780
I was sent by His Majesty

21
00:01:37,980 --> 00:01:39,259
to ensure your safety.

22
00:01:39,260 --> 00:01:41,420
Chu Shan wishes me dead.

23
00:01:42,100 --> 00:01:43,899
Why would he protect me?

24
00:01:43,900 --> 00:01:45,780
Every word I speak is true.

25
00:01:45,900 --> 00:01:47,580
I wouldn't dare deceive you.

26
00:01:51,540 --> 00:01:52,699
After the Empress passed,

27
00:01:52,700 --> 00:01:54,459
Helian Shu seized full control

28
00:01:54,460 --> 00:01:56,060
of the army.

29
00:01:56,260 --> 00:01:58,580
If Xi and I were to fall,

30
00:01:59,180 --> 00:02:02,420
she would usurp the throne.

31
00:02:03,900 --> 00:02:05,220
Where is the princess now?

32
00:02:06,700 --> 00:02:07,980
The Golden Guards report

33
00:02:08,140 --> 00:02:09,059
that Chu Xihe

34
00:02:09,060 --> 00:02:10,100
is missing.

35
00:02:10,620 --> 00:02:12,220
On the day of the Empress's funeral,

36
00:02:12,820 --> 00:02:14,099
I used a secret medicine

37
00:02:14,100 --> 00:02:16,300
to fake her death before Helian Shu,

38
00:02:17,180 --> 00:02:19,220
then had trusted men escort her
out of the palace.

39
00:02:19,780 --> 00:02:22,100
I meant for her to stay hidden

40
00:02:22,620 --> 00:02:25,020
until the rebels were purged,

41
00:02:25,260 --> 00:02:28,300
then bring her back
to inherit the throne.

42
00:02:28,420 --> 00:02:32,100
But now, all the escorts have died,

43
00:02:34,100 --> 00:02:36,860
and she's vanished without a trace.

44
00:02:37,380 --> 00:02:40,300
Pei Xiao, find her

45
00:02:40,420 --> 00:02:41,700
and protect her.

46
00:02:43,340 --> 00:02:44,859
I will protect Her Highness

47
00:02:44,860 --> 00:02:46,100
at all costs.

48
00:02:47,500 --> 00:02:49,820
What game is he playing?

49
00:02:50,700 --> 00:02:52,419
Mother is gone.

50
00:02:52,420 --> 00:02:53,980
I was cast out of the palace.

51
00:02:54,500 --> 00:02:56,300
Could something have happened inside?

52
00:02:56,380 --> 00:02:57,580
I do not know.

53
00:02:58,060 --> 00:02:59,540
His Majesty only ordered me to find you

54
00:02:59,700 --> 00:03:01,740
and deliver
what the Empress left behind.

55
00:03:02,980 --> 00:03:04,099
Where is it?

56
00:03:04,100 --> 00:03:05,540
At the General's residence.

57
00:03:06,060 --> 00:03:08,860
I humbly ask you
to return with me, Your Highness.

58
00:03:09,540 --> 00:03:11,100
You've already found her.

59
00:03:11,380 --> 00:03:13,180
Just bring it here.

60
00:03:15,660 --> 00:03:16,980
It's of great importance.

61
00:03:17,540 --> 00:03:18,980
If anything happens,

62
00:03:20,220 --> 00:03:21,939
who will answer for it?

63
00:03:21,940 --> 00:03:23,740
Pei Xiao and I grew up together.

64
00:03:23,980 --> 00:03:25,300
He wouldn't lie to me.

65
00:03:28,100 --> 00:03:29,740
If you're worried,

66
00:03:30,060 --> 00:03:31,660
you may come with me.

67
00:03:36,660 --> 00:03:38,020
I don't like mortals.

68
00:03:38,980 --> 00:03:40,460
Go if you wish.

69
00:03:46,820 --> 00:03:49,980
Then once you've refined the bone,

70
00:03:50,540 --> 00:03:52,140
come find me at the General's residence.

71
00:04:05,575 --> 00:04:08,720
(Qingxin Pavilion)

72
00:04:15,980 --> 00:04:18,260
She's finally out.

73
00:04:18,660 --> 00:04:19,700
Immortal,

74
00:04:20,260 --> 00:04:22,300
the plan to lure them out using Pei Xiao

75
00:04:22,380 --> 00:04:23,580
was mine.

76
00:04:24,100 --> 00:04:25,740
Don't forget what you promised me.

77
00:04:25,820 --> 00:04:29,140
No need to rush, Your Grace.

78
00:04:30,100 --> 00:04:31,300
Success

79
00:04:31,660 --> 00:04:33,460
depends on the next move.

80
00:04:33,580 --> 00:04:35,379
Nearly all of Ning's forces

81
00:04:35,380 --> 00:04:36,980
are under my control now.

82
00:04:37,660 --> 00:04:39,259
Once Chu Shan and Chu Xihe are dead,

83
00:04:39,260 --> 00:04:41,099
I'll rise and claim

84
00:04:41,100 --> 00:04:42,419
the throne.

85
00:04:42,420 --> 00:04:45,300
Then I'll name you State Preceptor,

86
00:04:45,700 --> 00:04:48,300
and we'll conquer the world together.

87
00:04:51,380 --> 00:04:53,300
Surely you jest, Your Grace.

88
00:04:54,220 --> 00:04:56,019
A mere throne

89
00:04:56,020 --> 00:04:57,980
is nothing.

90
00:04:58,540 --> 00:05:00,420
Once Chu Xihe is captured,

91
00:05:00,580 --> 00:05:02,019
we'll use her

92
00:05:02,020 --> 00:05:03,899
to cure your Verdant Decay.

93
00:05:03,900 --> 00:05:05,900
Then you'll be like me

94
00:05:06,340 --> 00:05:09,100
and become immortal.

95
00:05:10,460 --> 00:05:12,780
Wouldn't that be wonderful?

96
00:05:14,700 --> 00:05:16,100
Immortal?

97
00:05:17,780 --> 00:05:19,020
Immortal?

98
00:05:19,220 --> 00:05:20,340
Really?

99
00:05:20,580 --> 00:05:22,660
That is the dream of all
through the ages.

100
00:05:24,540 --> 00:05:27,020
Without ten thousand years of life,

101
00:05:27,580 --> 00:05:30,020
what is the point of being human?

102
00:05:36,340 --> 00:05:37,979
Where is what Mother left me?

103
00:05:37,980 --> 00:05:38,980
Inside.

104
00:05:45,337 --> 00:05:47,182
(From Empress Helian Ning)

105
00:05:48,580 --> 00:05:51,140
(To my child, open this personally.)

106
00:05:51,780 --> 00:05:53,460
(Are you well, Xihe?)

107
00:05:53,820 --> 00:05:57,020
(I won't be able
to spend New Year with you anymore.)

108
00:05:57,220 --> 00:05:58,779
(But I've had your father)

109
00:05:58,780 --> 00:06:01,339
(prepare your gifts
and clothes every year.)

110
00:06:01,340 --> 00:06:03,540
(Take them as my gift.)

111
00:06:04,020 --> 00:06:05,979
(Even in writing,)

112
00:06:05,980 --> 00:06:07,459
(writing these sentimental words)

113
00:06:07,460 --> 00:06:09,460
(Helian Ningshu)
(feels too awkward for me.)

114
00:06:09,900 --> 00:06:12,900
(But in the end,
it comes down to one wish.)

115
00:06:13,380 --> 00:06:16,580
(May you be blessed in every way,)

116
00:06:16,780 --> 00:06:19,220
(year after year.)

117
00:06:19,580 --> 00:06:22,580
(And don't blame your father.)

118
00:06:22,660 --> 00:06:25,540
(He loves you more than you know.)

119
00:06:31,087 --> 00:06:33,182
(On the day of the Empress's funeral)

120
00:07:21,220 --> 00:07:22,659
Everyone leave

121
00:07:22,660 --> 00:07:24,300
except for the young duke.

122
00:07:25,020 --> 00:07:26,060
Yes, Your Majesty.

123
00:07:33,100 --> 00:07:34,620
Your Majesty.

124
00:07:35,980 --> 00:07:38,060
How did my mother die?

125
00:07:39,340 --> 00:07:41,019
She was struck by miasma

126
00:07:41,020 --> 00:07:42,420
during a campaign,

127
00:07:43,100 --> 00:07:44,539
and passed upon returning.

128
00:07:44,540 --> 00:07:45,979
Mother

129
00:07:45,980 --> 00:07:47,019
was undefeated.

130
00:07:47,020 --> 00:07:48,860
How could she fall to that?

131
00:07:50,460 --> 00:07:53,420
She had long suffered from illness.

132
00:07:57,300 --> 00:07:59,219
You knew yet still sent her

133
00:07:59,220 --> 00:08:01,299
to war again and again.

134
00:08:01,300 --> 00:08:03,179
Now she's dead,

135
00:08:03,180 --> 00:08:04,419
and you think

136
00:08:04,420 --> 00:08:05,419
a few rituals

137
00:08:05,420 --> 00:08:07,420
will bring her back?

138
00:08:09,100 --> 00:08:11,060
What a joke.

139
00:08:11,420 --> 00:08:13,980
What use is this act after her death?

140
00:08:14,860 --> 00:08:17,060
You're not mourning her.

141
00:08:17,100 --> 00:08:18,980
You're easing your own conscience.

142
00:08:19,220 --> 00:08:20,060
Silence!

143
00:08:21,100 --> 00:08:22,780
If she hadn't given birth to you,

144
00:08:23,380 --> 00:08:24,380
her health

145
00:08:25,100 --> 00:08:26,980
wouldn't have suffered like this!

146
00:08:30,100 --> 00:08:32,620
Did I choose to be born?

147
00:08:33,780 --> 00:08:35,540
You gave me life,

148
00:08:35,580 --> 00:08:36,740
raised me,

149
00:08:37,650 --> 00:08:39,659
but never loved me.

150
00:08:39,660 --> 00:08:41,860
You imprisoned me again and again.

151
00:08:42,180 --> 00:08:44,060
Is this what being a father means?

152
00:08:44,980 --> 00:08:46,219
Insolence!

153
00:08:46,220 --> 00:08:47,860
You've lost all sense of propriety!

154
00:08:55,780 --> 00:08:57,460
Why are you laughing?

155
00:09:21,140 --> 00:09:22,260
Your Majesty,

156
00:09:22,700 --> 00:09:23,980
she's dead.

157
00:09:24,140 --> 00:09:25,259
I should've killed

158
00:09:25,260 --> 00:09:27,620
this ill-omened girl twenty years ago.

159
00:09:28,260 --> 00:09:29,059
Guards!

160
00:09:29,060 --> 00:09:29,740
Yes!

161
00:09:30,020 --> 00:09:31,339
Throw her out of the palace.

162
00:09:31,340 --> 00:09:32,220
Yes, Your Majesty.

163
00:09:41,180 --> 00:09:44,260
On New Year's Eve, no household sleeps,

164
00:09:44,980 --> 00:09:47,660
yet longing cannot reach through dreams.

165
00:09:49,100 --> 00:09:51,620
I wish I could spend New Year
with my mother.

166
00:09:54,620 --> 00:09:54,939
Father.

167
00:09:54,940 --> 00:09:56,300
You brat.

168
00:09:56,540 --> 00:09:58,300
Show some backbone.

169
00:09:58,740 --> 00:10:00,620
Isn't spending it with me enough?

170
00:10:00,740 --> 00:10:02,299
It's not that,

171
00:10:02,300 --> 00:10:04,500
but who spends New Year in prison?

172
00:10:04,740 --> 00:10:06,299
Haven't you seen?

173
00:10:06,300 --> 00:10:08,420
Ning Capital's finally peaceful.

174
00:10:08,660 --> 00:10:09,779
As long as we guard

175
00:10:09,780 --> 00:10:11,180
this prison tight,

176
00:10:11,420 --> 00:10:14,300
the people can have a safe New Year.

177
00:10:14,420 --> 00:10:16,180
Look at these Flower Slaves.

178
00:10:16,540 --> 00:10:18,940
They haven't tasted flesh in days.

179
00:10:19,420 --> 00:10:21,420
If they escape,

180
00:10:21,660 --> 00:10:23,420
they'll devour

181
00:10:23,540 --> 00:10:25,180
the entire city.

182
00:10:33,100 --> 00:10:35,940
Father, what are they doing?

183
00:10:39,740 --> 00:10:42,180
Father, their eyes are glowing red!

184
00:10:55,860 --> 00:10:57,219
Go report to the General.

185
00:10:57,220 --> 00:10:58,219
I'll hold them here.

186
00:10:58,220 --> 00:10:59,659
I won't let them escape.

187
00:10:59,660 --> 00:11:00,539
I'm not leaving!

188
00:11:00,540 --> 00:11:01,619
Go!

189
00:11:01,620 --> 00:11:03,420
I won't leave you!

190
00:11:03,940 --> 00:11:04,859
I won't leave you!

191
00:11:04,860 --> 00:11:06,100
Go!

192
00:11:08,420 --> 00:11:09,860
I'll be back, Father!

193
00:11:14,500 --> 00:11:15,620
General!

194
00:11:17,780 --> 00:11:18,619
General!

195
00:11:18,620 --> 00:11:19,099
Chengjiang!

196
00:11:19,100 --> 00:11:20,979
General, bad news!

197
00:11:20,980 --> 00:11:22,339
There's trouble at the prison!

198
00:11:22,340 --> 00:11:23,659
The Flower Slaves seized the keys

199
00:11:23,660 --> 00:11:25,540
and are breaking out!

200
00:11:25,660 --> 00:11:26,859
What?

201
00:11:26,860 --> 00:11:28,180
How many of them are in the prison?

202
00:11:29,340 --> 00:11:30,299
Your Highness,

203
00:11:30,300 --> 00:11:31,940
no fewer than five hundred.

204
00:11:32,860 --> 00:11:33,980
Lead the way.

205
00:11:34,180 --> 00:11:34,979
Your Highness!

206
00:11:34,980 --> 00:11:37,339
(Lingyun Pavilion)
Don't talk to me about danger.

207
00:11:37,340 --> 00:11:38,499
If they escape,

208
00:11:38,500 --> 00:11:39,820
Ning will be in real danger.

209
00:11:40,060 --> 00:11:41,059
We'll go first.

210
00:11:41,060 --> 00:11:42,299
Summon the Pei army

211
00:11:42,300 --> 00:11:43,299
and stop them.

212
00:11:43,300 --> 00:11:44,260
Yes!

213
00:11:48,740 --> 00:11:49,860
Father!

214
00:11:55,980 --> 00:11:57,940
Do whatever it takes to catch her!

215
00:12:36,300 --> 00:12:38,220
Ye Zhao, come out!

216
00:12:50,180 --> 00:12:51,740
How did you know I was here?

217
00:12:52,180 --> 00:12:53,220
Ally.

218
00:12:53,300 --> 00:12:55,020
I knew you were here all along.

219
00:12:55,260 --> 00:12:56,460
Ally.

220
00:13:00,780 --> 00:13:01,860
Master.

221
00:13:16,625 --> 00:13:18,334
♪Too bad the rain will stop♪

222
00:13:18,335 --> 00:13:21,184
♪The wind will fade,
tomorrow will clear♪

223
00:13:21,185 --> 00:13:23,924
♪I'd rather this night never end♪

224
00:13:23,925 --> 00:13:25,554
♪Let the long shadows♪

225
00:13:25,555 --> 00:13:31,155
♪whisper what's in your heart♪

226
00:13:31,205 --> 00:13:32,804
♪If in a dream♪

227
00:13:32,805 --> 00:13:35,564
♪I can hear your voice♪

228
00:13:35,565 --> 00:13:38,414
♪Then let it be our meeting♪

229
00:13:38,415 --> 00:13:41,014
♪Let it be us♪

230
00:13:41,015 --> 00:13:45,804
♪drawing endlessly close♪

231
00:13:45,805 --> 00:13:47,564
♪Too bad the rain will stop♪

232
00:13:47,565 --> 00:13:50,215
♪The wind will fade,
tomorrow will clear♪

233
00:13:50,435 --> 00:13:53,154
♪I can't even hold you properly♪

234
00:13:53,155 --> 00:13:54,804
♪Not even in time♪

235
00:13:54,805 --> 00:14:00,464
♪to tell you how I feel♪

236
00:14:00,465 --> 00:14:02,004
♪If the rain won't stop♪

237
00:14:02,005 --> 00:14:04,754
♪If the wind won't fade,
if time stands still♪

238
00:14:04,755 --> 00:14:07,724
♪Let love go on♪

239
00:14:07,725 --> 00:14:10,274
♪Until forever♪

240
00:14:10,275 --> 00:14:14,914
♪Until we slowly grow old♪

241
00:14:14,915 --> 00:14:17,524
♪Until forever♪

242
00:14:17,525 --> 00:14:24,635
♪Until we slowly grow old♪
